function info($str) { echo "INFO: $str\n"; }
function warn($str) { echo "WARNING: $str\n"; }
function err($str) { die("FATAL ERROR: $str\n"); }

@set_time_limit(0);

@header('Content-Type: text/plain');

chdir(__DIR__);
$cont = @file_get_contents('changelog.json.php');
if ($cont === false) err('Cannot read changelog.json.php');
$json = @json_decode($cont, true);
if ($json === null) err('Cannot parse changelog.json.php');
$latest_version = false;
foreach ($json as $v) {
	if (isset($v['version']) && (substr($v['version'], -4) != '-dev')) {
		$latest_version = $v['version'];
		break; // the first item is the latest version
	}
}
if ($latest_version != '2.0.1.13') err('This update can only be applied to OIDplus version 2.0.1.13!');

if (version_compare(PHP_VERSION, '7.0.0') < 0) {
	err('You need PHP Version 7.0 to update to this version');
}

if (!is_file('changelog.json.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: changelog.json.php');
	writefile_1();
	if (!is_file('changelog.json.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): changelog.json.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('changelog.json.php') != '57beabb69460e2b1aab920bb5f9fdad2abf18064') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): changelog.json.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('changelog.json.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of changelog.json.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('changelog.json.php') !== '57beabb69460e2b1aab920bb5f9fdad2abf18064') {
		if (@sha1_file('changelog.json.php') !== 'f55b9196e4c3aa2a48f93808fada0ba9ec053909') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: changelog.json.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('changelog.json.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('changelog.json.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('changelog.json.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_1();
		if (@sha1_file('changelog.json.php') !== '57beabb69460e2b1aab920bb5f9fdad2abf18064') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): changelog.json.php');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('includes/classes/OIDplusDatabaseConnection.class.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: includes/classes/OIDplusDatabaseConnection.class.php');
	writefile_2();
	if (!is_file('includes/classes/OIDplusDatabaseConnection.class.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): includes/classes/OIDplusDatabaseConnection.class.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusDatabaseConnection.class.php') != '6450aa791f25ade48199e9a87f148827b89dce3f') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/OIDplusDatabaseConnection.class.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('includes/classes/OIDplusDatabaseConnection.class.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of includes/classes/OIDplusDatabaseConnection.class.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusDatabaseConnection.class.php') !== '6450aa791f25ade48199e9a87f148827b89dce3f') {
		if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusDatabaseConnection.class.php') !== '549778a0749084e6e6c3debaf31ca0fe04ffc4c9') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: includes/classes/OIDplusDatabaseConnection.class.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('includes/classes/OIDplusDatabaseConnection.class.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('includes/classes/OIDplusDatabaseConnection.class.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('includes/classes/OIDplusDatabaseConnection.class.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_2();
		if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusDatabaseConnection.class.php') !== '6450aa791f25ade48199e9a87f148827b89dce3f') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/OIDplusDatabaseConnection.class.php');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php');
	writefile_3();
	if (!is_file('includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php') != '00f4288dea5cc28269ba1b824658547dcc869544') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php') !== '00f4288dea5cc28269ba1b824658547dcc869544') {
		if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php') !== '20772d15c19acc751b4b75a5232975b6dee103d8') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_3();
		if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php') !== '00f4288dea5cc28269ba1b824658547dcc869544') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php');
		}
	}
}

	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: includes/classes/OIDplusObject.class.php');
	writefile_4();
	if (!is_file('includes/classes/OIDplusObject.class.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): includes/classes/OIDplusObject.class.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusObject.class.php') != '98b47a507c86338fe52150fba42f91bf5893f0f1') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/OIDplusObject.class.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('includes/classes/OIDplusObject.class.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of includes/classes/OIDplusObject.class.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusObject.class.php') !== '98b47a507c86338fe52150fba42f91bf5893f0f1') {
		if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusObject.class.php') !== '78a3921c8f7d3644efe05d8089134f1b49994352') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: includes/classes/OIDplusObject.class.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('includes/classes/OIDplusObject.class.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('includes/classes/OIDplusObject.class.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('includes/classes/OIDplusObject.class.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_4();
		if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusObject.class.php') !== '98b47a507c86338fe52150fba42f91bf5893f0f1') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/OIDplusObject.class.php');
		}
	}
}

			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/viathinksoft/database/odbc/OIDplusQueryResultODBC.class.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_11();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/database/odbc/OIDplusQueryResultODBC.class.php') !== 'ccfdcecb05a4f3da9a851ba64ed44dfb378d0714') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/database/odbc/OIDplusQueryResultODBC.class.php');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml');
	writefile_13();
	if (!is_file('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml') != '8915f29537334b84e747fd03da22895d05491aff') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml') !== '8915f29537334b84e747fd03da22895d05491aff') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml') !== 'ddc9163dae7be9dc9a5fc975e9024663cb48f07d') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_13();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml') !== '8915f29537334b84e747fd03da22895d05491aff') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('vendor/composer/installed.json')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: vendor/composer/installed.json');
	writefile_15();
	if (!is_file('vendor/composer/installed.json')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): vendor/composer/installed.json');
	} else if (sha1_file('vendor/composer/installed.json') != '858858377d8c8e47b3427e8e25a7e1281a58176b') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): vendor/composer/installed.json');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('vendor/composer/installed.json', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of vendor/composer/installed.json');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('vendor/composer/installed.json') !== '858858377d8c8e47b3427e8e25a7e1281a58176b') {
		if (@sha1_file('vendor/composer/installed.json') !== '48a67bc9b63f78d2ef5f2e1af79a827f178f556b') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: vendor/composer/installed.json');
			$tmp = pathinfo('vendor/composer/installed.json');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('vendor/composer/installed.json')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('vendor/composer/installed.json', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_15();
		if (@sha1_file('vendor/composer/installed.json') !== '858858377d8c8e47b3427e8e25a7e1281a58176b') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): vendor/composer/installed.json');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('vendor/composer/installed.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: vendor/composer/installed.php');
	writefile_16();
	if (!is_file('vendor/composer/installed.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): vendor/composer/installed.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('vendor/composer/installed.php') != 'aa29b8195a4b148d59b0a735bfa7293523fd842b') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): vendor/composer/installed.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('vendor/composer/installed.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of vendor/composer/installed.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('vendor/composer/installed.php') !== 'aa29b8195a4b148d59b0a735bfa7293523fd842b') {
		if (@sha1_file('vendor/composer/installed.php') !== 'fdf99db6a156e409c4f741ccd1f2be340a77837f') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: vendor/composer/installed.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('vendor/composer/installed.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('vendor/composer/installed.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('vendor/composer/installed.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_16();
		if (@sha1_file('vendor/composer/installed.php') !== 'aa29b8195a4b148d59b0a735bfa7293523fd842b') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): vendor/composer/installed.php');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('vendor/licenses')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: vendor/licenses');
	writefile_17();
	if (!is_file('vendor/licenses')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): vendor/licenses');
	} else if (sha1_file('vendor/licenses') != '42d42049ec1f47451b632d412e83da9cfc4e9189') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): vendor/licenses');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('vendor/licenses', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of vendor/licenses');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('vendor/licenses') !== '42d42049ec1f47451b632d412e83da9cfc4e9189') {
		if (@sha1_file('vendor/licenses') !== '71461d97a39e1d54ac163a19d78a6a478a2b5198') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: vendor/licenses');
			$tmp = pathinfo('vendor/licenses');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('vendor/licenses')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('vendor/licenses', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_17();
		if (@sha1_file('vendor/licenses') !== '42d42049ec1f47451b632d412e83da9cfc4e9189') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): vendor/licenses');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('vendor/phpseclib/phpseclib/phpseclib/Net/SFTP.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: vendor/phpseclib/phpseclib/phpseclib/Net/SFTP.php');
	writefile_18();
	if (!is_file('vendor/phpseclib/phpseclib/phpseclib/Net/SFTP.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): vendor/phpseclib/phpseclib/phpseclib/Net/SFTP.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('vendor/phpseclib/phpseclib/phpseclib/Net/SFTP.php') != '85b15ffcd00f541ac8bcce370bed4a6ff26a50ce') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): vendor/phpseclib/phpseclib/phpseclib/Net/SFTP.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('vendor/phpseclib/phpseclib/phpseclib/Net/SFTP.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of vendor/phpseclib/phpseclib/phpseclib/Net/SFTP.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('vendor/phpseclib/phpseclib/phpseclib/Net/SFTP.php') !== '85b15ffcd00f541ac8bcce370bed4a6ff26a50ce') {
		if (@sha1_file('vendor/phpseclib/phpseclib/phpseclib/Net/SFTP.php') !== '7789492b33d38665568d406965869ca7c55ec01d') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: vendor/phpseclib/phpseclib/phpseclib/Net/SFTP.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('vendor/phpseclib/phpseclib/phpseclib/Net/SFTP.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('vendor/phpseclib/phpseclib/phpseclib/Net/SFTP.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('vendor/phpseclib/phpseclib/phpseclib/Net/SFTP.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_18();
		if (@sha1_file('vendor/phpseclib/phpseclib/phpseclib/Net/SFTP.php') !== '85b15ffcd00f541ac8bcce370bed4a6ff26a50ce') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): vendor/phpseclib/phpseclib/phpseclib/Net/SFTP.php');
		}
	}
